\id 2PE 2 Peter in Boko, Ross Jones 2/08
\h 2 Piɛɛ
\toc1 Piɛɛ lá plaade
\toc2 2 Piɛɛ
\toc3 2Piɛ
\mt1 PIƐƐ LÁ PLAADE
\imt1 Yã́ pↄ́ kú láɛ bee guuↄ
\ip Piɛɛ láɛ bee kɛ̃̀ Yesu náaikɛnaↄnɛ ḿpii (1.1). Aà yã́zĩnda mɛ́ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ an yã́ lí kↄ̃sɛ ń Yesu baonaoo ɛɛboa ũ. An yãdanɛↄ ì mↄ́ ń yãyaaaoɛ. Tó gbɛ̃́ ye kɛ̃́má, sema aà azĩa kpa Lua dↄ̃a sĩandewa ń Yesu Kilisi yã́o lá gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ wɛsìaàlɛↄ òwa.
\ip Fↄkpaamá gbɛa (1.1-2) a dìdi Yesudekɛyãↄwa ń dɛa náaideↄ ũ Luaɛ lá gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa wɛsì Diilɛↄ òwa (1.3-21). Bee gbɛa à waasokɛn ɛgɛnaↄ yãkɛaↄ ń ń kuao bɛ̃̀ɛbò maamaa (2.1-22). À ń yãdanɛ taa ò lɛɛ àaↄ̃ guu, à mɛ̀ aaìↄ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aalɛ Kilisi mↄa dãↄ laanikɛɛ, aaì mɛ Kilisi a ɛa mↄ lↄo. Piɛɛ mɛ̀ tó Kilisi mↄa lɛ́ gɛ̃gɛ̃, Lua mɛnakɛa yã́iɛ, asa a ye dasi zɛ'e aa Yesu náaikɛ.
\ip Waasonkɛn ɛgɛnaↄ lí kɛ̃́sã dṹniau gueio. Piɛɛ lá plaade yãdanɛá tia yã́ɛ lↄ, àlɛ tɛ́kpa luanaaikɛnaↄgu aa gɛ́ aɛ Dii dↄ̃a guu, kɛ́ aasu zã zɛ́wao yã́i.
\c 1
\s1 Sĩanakpaa sísia pↄ́ Lua wá sisiwa
\p 
\v 1 Mámɛmaa Lua zĩna Simↄↄ Piɛɛ, Yesu Kilisi zↄ̀blena, mámɛ ma láɛ bee kɛ̃̀ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ wá Lua wá Suabana Yesu Kilisi ń gbá zɛ́ aa a náaikɛ̀ láwáwa a maakɛ yã́iↄnɛ.
\v 2 Gbɛ̃kɛ ń aafiao pɛɛwá Lua ń wá Dii Yesuo dↄ̃a guu.
\p 
\v 3 Lua wá sɛ́ wàↄ ku a gawi ń a maakɛo guuɛ, a tò wà a dↄ̃, ↄ̃ aà luakɛgbãa wá gbá pↄ́ pↄ́ dɛ wàↄ vĩ, wá kua i kpaaĩ ń aà yã́o.
\v 4 Beewa à yãzↄ̃ↄ bɛɛɛde pↄ́ à a lɛgbɛ̃̀ kɛ̀wɛ̃ɛ, kɛ́ a yã́i wà bↄ dṹnia dↄ́ɛ'ĩi pↄ́ ì ń ↄ̃̀ↄkpa guu, wíↄ Lua dàa vĩ.
\v 5 Yã́ bee yã́i à ãiakɛ maamaa, à Lua náaikɛ maakɛa guu, í yãmaakɛ Lua yãdↄ̃a guu,
\v 6 íↄ Lua yã́ dↄ̃ ázĩa kũa dↄ̃ guu, íↄ ázĩa kũa dↄ̃ mɛna guu, íↄ mɛna vĩ naa Luawa guu,
\v 7 íↄ naa Luawa kↄ̃gbɛ̃kɛ guu, íↄ gbɛ̃kɛ vĩ ń kↄ̃o ń yeakↄ̃io.
\v 8 Asa tó á yã́ beeↄ kũa mɛ́ aalɛ kã́fĩɛ́, áↄ ku pã wá Dii Yesu Kilisi dↄ̃a kã́fĩaɛ́ saio.
\v 9 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ yã́ beeↄ kũa sↄ̃o, à a wɛ́ kũ̀aa à gↄ̃̀ vĩ̀a ũɛ. Kɛ́ Lua duuna pↄ́ a kɛ̀ yãaↄ kɛ̃̀wà, à sã̀aàguɛ.
\v 10 Ayãmɛto ma gbɛ̃́ↄ, à ãiakɛ à gbãakpa sísia pↄ́ Lua á sisi à á sɛ́wa. Tó álɛ yã́ beeↄ kɛ, á fu bauo.
\v 11 Beewa wa gbãakpaázi maamaa, íↄ kú ń wá Dii wá Suabana Yesu Kilisio aà kpala pↄ́ lí láao guu.
\p 
\v 12 Ayãmɛto baa kɛ́ á yã́ beeↄ dↄ̃, mɛ́ á zɛdↄa sĩana pↄ́ á kũa guu, máↄ yã́piↄ dↄáguɛ.
\v 13 Gↄↄ pↄ́ má kú ma sↄ guu, málɛ e a maa màↄ tɛ́kpaágu yã́piↄ dↄaágu guuɛ.
\v 14 Má dↄ̃ kɛ́ ma bↄa ma sↄu gↄↄ a ka tia, lá wá Dii Yesu Kilisi dↄ̀aa òmɛɛwa.
\v 15 Má ãiakɛ, kɛ́ yã́piↄ e àↄ dↄágu gↄↄpii ma gaa gbɛaɛ.
\s1 Sĩanakpaa ãnabiↄ yã́wa
\p 
\v 16 Kɛ́ wa wá Dii Yesu Kilisi mↄa ń gbãao òɛ́, i kɛ wá tɛ́ fĩ pↄ́ wa dà ń kↄ̃niozi no. Wa wɛsì aà zↄ̃ↄkɛlɛɛ,
\v 17 gↄↄ pↄ́ Mae Lua aà kpɛlà à aà tↄbↄ̀. À Zↄ̃ↄde Gawide lↄↄ mà à mɛ̀ a Nɛ́ mɛ̀ndona yenziden aà ũ, aà yã́ ì kaagu.
\v 18 Wa lↄↄ pↄ́ bↄ̀ luabɛpi mà gↄↄ pↄ́ wá kuaànↄ gbɛ̀sĩsĩ pↄ́ a kua adoa musu.\f + \fr 1.18 \ft Mat 17.1-5\f*
\v 19 Bee yã́ pↄ́ ãnabiↄ ò sĩanapìliwànɛ́. A maa à laaidↄ yã́piwa filia pↄ́ lɛ́ guduuduu pu ũɛ e gudↄlɛia saana àↄ gɛ́ bilɛi á sↄ̃u, gu i dↄɛ́.
\v 20 Àↄ dↄ̃ gĩa kɛ́ gbɛ̃e lí fↄ̃ yã́ pↄ́ ãnabi kɛ̃̀ láu bↄↄlɛkɛ̀ ń azĩaoo.
\v 21 Ãnabiↄ yãe lí bↄ gbɛ̃nazĩna pↄeã guuo, aa Lua yã'ò lá aà Nisĩna dↄ̀aanɛ́waɛ.
\c 2
\s1 Waasokɛn ɛgɛnaↄ
\p 
\v 1 Ãnabi ɛgɛnaↄ bↄ̀ yãa Isailiↄ guu. Beewa waasokɛn ɛgɛnaↄ bↄ á guu lↄ, aai ɛɛ pↄ́ ì to wà kaalɛ ká Lua yãdanɛu, aai lelekpa Dii pↄ́ ń bózi, aai ńzĩa kaalɛ kã́ndo.
\v 2 Wa tɛ́ńzi dasi an wisaiyãkɛa guu, wi sĩana zɛ́ bɛ̃̀ɛbo an yã́i.
\v 3 An bĩikɛa guu aa á ble ń ɛɛ pↄ́ aaì blewào. Yã́kpalɛ zↄ̃̀lɛmá à gɛ̃̀gɛ̃, i lí na ń Kàalɛna wɛ́uo.
\p 
\v 4 Asa Lua i malaika pↄ́ duunakɛ̀ↄ too, à ń ká gbã́o sia pↄ́ kú zĩ́lɛzĩlɛ guu, àↄ ń kũa e yã́kpalɛkɛgↄↄzĩɛ.
\v 5 I dṹnia zi ń a yãdansai pↄ́ kú a guuↄ too, a tò í dàńla. Ãma à Nↄee pↄ́ ì maakɛa waasokɛ bↄ̀ ń a gbɛ̃́ gbɛ̃ↄn soplaↄ.\f + \fr 2.5 \ft Daa 6.1-7.24\f*
\v 6 À yãdà Sↄdↄũ ń Gↄmↄↄola,\f + \fr 2.6 \ft Daa 19.24\f* à ń kaalɛ aa gↄ̃̀ túfu ũ yã́ pↄ́ a luayãdansaiↄ le seela ũ.
\v 7 Ãma à Lↄtu bↄ̀. A dɛ gbɛ̃maa ũ, aà nↄ̀sɛ ↄ̃̀ↄkpà ikoyãdansaipiↄ wisaiyãkɛa yã́i.\f + \fr 2.7 \ft Daa 19.12-17\f*
\v 8 Gbɛ̃maapi kú ń guuɛ, yãvãi pↄ́ àlɛ e àlɛ ma lá gu lɛ́ dↄ aà wã̀wã aà nↄ̀sɛmaa yã́i.
\v 9 Màa Dii gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ naawa bↄa yↄ̃a guu dↄ̃, mɛ́ a gbɛ̃vãi kũa dↄ̃ e àↄ gɛ́ ĩadaiwà yã́kpalɛkɛgↄↄzĩ.
\v 10 Atɛ̃sa gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aaì saka ikoyãu, an mɛ̀ dↄ́ɛ'ĩiↄ ì dↄaanɛ́ gbãsĩkɛa guuↄ.
\p Waasokɛn ɛgɛnapiↄá sↄ̃gbãade kàamaideↄnɛ. Dↄ́ɛa ń malaika gawideↄ lí ń vĩakũo.
\v 11 Malaika pↄ́ an gbãa ń ń ikoo dɛ waasokɛnapiↄlaↄ aali we ń tↄbɛ̃ɛsì aa gɛ̀ ń ń káalao Dii aɛo.
\v 12 Gbɛ̃́piↄ ì yã́ pↄ́ wa a gbadↄ̃o bɛ̃̀ɛboɛ. Gbɛ̃nazĩn báa mɛ́ dańla, aa làasoo vĩo. Wà ń í kɛ́ wà ń kṹ wà ń dɛ yã́iɛ. Aa kaalɛ lán nↄ̀bↄↄwaɛ,
\v 13 wi vãi pↄ́ aa kɛ̀ fĩabonɛ́. Dↄ́ɛ'ĩikɛa fãanɛ ì kɛnɛ́ yãna ũɛ. Gↄↄ pↄ́ aalɛ blɛbleánↄ, aaì pↄnakɛ ń ń kↄ̃nikɛanɛ́oɛ. An kua á guuá sãaɛ mɛ́ gbãsĩɛ.
\v 14 An wɛ́ ìↄ pɛa nↄɛ dↄ́ɛ'ĩideↄwa, duuna lí mↄ́máo. Aaì kↄ̃nikɛ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ Lua yã́ i zɛdↄ ń guuoↄnɛ. Bĩi ń sↄ̃ pà. Lua lɛkɛ̀nɛ́ɛ.
\v 15 Aa sã̀sã, aa kɛ̃̀ zɛ́ súsuwa, aa zɛ́ doũ sɛ̀ ń Bɛↄↄ nɛ́ Balaaũ pↄ́ ye ↄbɛ̃ɛio.
\v 16 Zàa'ĩna a pↄ́lɛbũu'ia à yã'òɛ̀ lán gbɛ̃nazĩnawa, à aà gbà laai aà vãikɛa musu, à gìɛ̀ ń aà mìsaiyãkɛao.\f + \fr 2.16 \ft Nao 22.4-35\f*
\v 17 Gbɛ̃́ beeↄ dɛ lán nibↄna pↄ́ a í bàwaɛ, lán lousisia pↄ́ gɛ̃̀zɛa ń ĩ́anaowa. Gusia níinii ↄ̃ Lua dìlɛnɛ́ yàae ũ.
\v 18 Aaì ĩ́an gii zↄ̃ↄ dã, aaì kↄ̃nikɛ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa bↄ̀ sã́sãzɛu dafuↄnɛ ń dↄ́ɛ'ĩio ń wisaiyão.
\v 19 Yã́ pↄ́ ì ń ↄ̃̀ↄkpa zↄↄn ń ũ, ↄ̃ aaì gↄ̃a wɛ̃́ɛↄ ũ lɛgbɛ̃nɛ́. Asa gbɛ̃́pii dɛ yã́ pↄ́ a sↄ̃ blè zↄ ũɛ.
\p 
\v 20 Tó aa bↄ̀ dṹnia gbãsĩkɛau wá Dii wá Suabana Yesu Kilisi dↄ̃a sabai, mɛ́ aa tò yã́pi ɛ̀a yèelɛmá à ń sↄ̃ blè, an kua gbɛzã vãi ìↄ dɛ a káaua.
\v 21 Tó aai zɛ́ súsu dↄ̃ yãao, bee maańnↄ dɛ kɛ́ aa dↄ̃̀ aa gbàsa bↄ̀ Lua yã́ pↄ́ wa dànɛ́ kpɛla.
\v 22 Yáasi pↄ́ wa kɛ̀ɛ beeↄ sĩana sùmá: Gbɛ̃ ì ɛa pↄ́ pↄ́ a pìsi ble.\f + \fr 2.22 \ft Yaa 26.11\f* Beewa lↄ: Sàwakusana pↄ́ wà a zu'ò ì ɛa málɛ pɛ̀lɛau.
\c 3
\s1 Dii mↄ́zĩ
\p 
\v 1 Ma gbɛ̃́ yenzideↄ, lá plaade pↄ́ má kɛ̃̀ɛ́n kɛ. Ampii guu ma yã́ dↄ̀águ, kɛ́ à vu iu ń làasoo maaoɛ.
\v 2 Má ye yã́ pↄ́ Lua ãnabiↄ ò yãaↄ dↄágu ń yã́ pↄ́ Dii wá Suabana dìlɛ a zĩnaↄnɛ aa òɛ́o.
\v 3 Àↄ dↄ̃ za káau kɛ́ gↄↄgbɛzãzĩ zĩapↄeãkɛnaↄ mↄ á kɛ pↄ́ↄpↄↄ\f + \fr 3.3 \ft Yud 18\f*
\v 4 aa mɛ: I a mↄa lɛgbɛ̃o lé? A ku má ni? Wá maeↄ gàga, kási pↄ́pii kú a gbɛu lá Lua dṹnia kàlɛwaɛ.
\v 5 Kɛ́ Lua yã'ò yãa, à musu ń dṹniao kɛ̀, aa yã́pi kpà swã́aɛ. À tↄↄlɛ bↄ̀ íu, a ku ípi sabai,\f + \fr 3.5 \ft Daa 1.6-9\f*
\v 6 ípi mɛ́ dà dṹnia káaua à kàalɛ.\f + \fr 3.6 \ft Daa 7.11\f*
\v 7 Lua yã'oa doũpi mɛ́ tò musu ń dṹnia tiaɛ beeo dilɛa tɛ́ pↄ́ ũ e gↄↄ pↄ́ a yã́kpalɛkɛ ń a yãdansaiↄ, i ń kaalɛ.\f + \fr 3.7 \ft Isa 66.15-16\f*
\p 
\v 8 Ma gbɛ̃́ yenzideↄ, ásu to yã́ɛ bee sã́águo: Gↄↄ do dɛ Diiɛ lán wɛ̃̀ ↄ̀aa sↄowaɛ, mɛ́ wɛ̃̀ ↄ̀aa sↄo dɛɛ̀ lán gↄↄ dowa.\f + \fr 3.8 \ft Soũ 90.4\f*
\v 9 Dii zígbia ń yã́ pↄ́ à a lɛgbɛ̃̀ kɛao lá gbɛ̃eↄ lɛ́ ewao, àlɛ mɛnakɛánↄ. A ye gbɛ̃e kaalɛo, a ye gbɛ̃́pii nↄ̀sɛlilɛɛ.
\v 10 Dii mↄ́zĩ aↄ dɛ lán kpã́i mↄawaɛ.\f + \fr 3.10 \ft Mat 24.43, 1Tɛs 5.2, Zia 16.15\f* Zĩbeezĩ musu a gɛ̃zɛa bìoo, a pↄ́ↄ tɛ́kũ aa pia, tↄↄlɛ ń pↄ́ pↄ́ kuwàↄ aↄ ku lↄo.
\v 11 Lá pↄ́pii a kaalɛ màa, à tó á kua àↄ ku kua ũ. À tó á kua àↄ adoa luayãmanaↄ ũ
\v 12 wɛdↄa aà mↄgↄↄi, í wɛtã gↄↄpi ka kpakpa. Gↄↄpi zĩ́ musu a kaalɛ ń tɛ́o, a pusu i a pↄ́ↄ yↄ́.
\v 13 Ãma Lua tↄↄlɛ dafu ń luabɛ dafuo\f + \fr 3.13 \ft Isa 65.17, 66.22, Zia 21.1\f* lɛgbɛ̃̀, ↄ̃ wá wɛ́ dↄi. We maakɛa aↄ kuu.
\p 
\v 14 Ayãmɛto ma gbɛ̃́ yenzideↄ, wɛdↄa gↄↄpizi guu à ãiakɛ àↄ ku sãasai gbãsĩsai, íↄ na ń Luao.
\v 15 À wá Dii mɛnakɛa dilɛ suabaa ũ, lá wá gbɛ̃́ yenzide Pↄlu lakɛ̃̀ɛ́ ń ↄ̃nↄ pↄ́ Lua aà gbàowa.
\v 16 Yã́piↄ ↄ̃ Pↄlu ì o lá pↄ́ a kɛ̃̀ↄ guu píi. Aà lápi gueↄ maa zĩ'ũ. Wɛ́siadeↄ ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ an zɛa gbãaoↄ aaì yã́piↄ kole, lá aaì kɛ ń Luayãtaala kĩniↄwaɛ lↄ. Màa aaì ńzĩa da kaalɛu.
\p 
\v 17 Ápiↄ sↄ̃ ma gbɛ̃́ yenzideↄ, lá á yã́pi dↄ̃ kↄ̀, à laaika kɛ́ ikoyãdansaiↄ su á sã́sã ń ń ɛɛoo. Ásu bↄ á zɛa gbãau à lɛ́lɛo.
\v 18 Àↄ gbã wá Dii wá Suabana Yesu Kilisi gbɛ̃kɛ ń aà dↄ̃ao guu. Ɔ̃mɛ gawi vĩ tia e gↄↄpii! Ãmi.
